                     AUC = unlist(auc_list)
                     )
setorder(auc_df,Model)


ggplot(auc_df, aes(factor(Model), AUC*100, fill = factor(Sample))) + 
  geom_col(width=0.5,position=position_dodge(0.5))+
  coord_cartesian(ylim=c(50,floor(max(auc_df$AUC*100))+0.5))+
  scale_x_discrete(labels = c('Credit score','Basic model','Traditional model', 'Traditional model\n+alternative vars', 'Upstart model'))+
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("dodgerblue1","dodgerblue4"))+
  theme_minimal()+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom",legend.title = element_blank())+labs(x="",y="AUC")+
  geom_text(aes(label=round(AUC*100,1)), position=position_dodge(width=0.65), vjust=-0.25,size=3)
